snippet.title: Metal Freezer - Mame 0.174 - Shortplay
snippet.description:
Shortplay of Metal Freezer running on Mame 0.174. This game was recently dumped by MAMEDEV team and was made by Seibu Kaihatsu in 1989.
This was a rare game released on Japan so it is a really nice addition to the emulator.
